// --------------------------
// --- Character Identity ---
// --------------------------

// The character's core identity, including name, age, gender, species, and other defining traits.

character

// Identity encompasses all the fundamental attributes that define who the character is, including their name, age, gender, species, and other key characteristics that shape their identity and how they are perceived in the world.
  identity

