        description = Balanced, impartial, avoids extremes.
      chaotic_neutral
        description = Values personal freedom; unpredictable but not malicious.
      lawful_evil
        description = Uses order and structure for personal gain or control.
      neutral_evil
        description = Self‑serving, acting without regard for others.
      chaotic_evil
        description = Destructive, unpredictable, and driven by selfish impulses.

